pageContext.title: It’s Lake Shasta Time
pageContext.excerpt: Kinda like Peanut Butter Jelly, except “Lake Shasta” with maybe a sandwich of that kind for lunch? Look, I like Lake Shasta and really enjoy the productive fishing the largest reservoir in the State of California provides. Lake Shasta is the most rewarding rainbow trout trolling fishery right now.
